&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Conduct proactive outreach to existing customer contacts through persona based, tactical prospecting campaigns through all channels (phone, email, social media)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
