&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Implementation Consultant plays a critical role in ensuring the successful post-sales delivery of Documo’s products. This role focuses on onboarding, configuring, and implementing solutions for customers while driving adoption and long-term value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will partner closely with Customer Success, Product, and Sales teams to ensure smooth implementations, help customers achieve their desired outcomes, and provide technical guidance during the adoption process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Success in This Role Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successfully managing customer onboarding and implementation projects from kickoff to completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring customers are set up correctly and effectively using Documo products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with internal teams to address technical or process challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving as a trusted advisor during implementation and providing ongoing guidance for adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to customer satisfaction, retention, and long-term product value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliverables/Outcomes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Implementation &amp;amp; Onboarding&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead post-sales onboarding and implementation of Documo products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure solutions to meet customer requirements and business processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop project plans, timelines, and success criteria for each implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct technical workshops, training sessions, and knowledge transfer with customer teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and resolve potential technical or operational challenges during implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Enablement &amp;amp; Adoption&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure customers understand how to use Documo products effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance on best practices, workflows, and integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor adoption metrics and proactively address usage gaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect customer feedback to inform process improvements and product enhancements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
