&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Documo is seeking an Inside Sales Representative to join our growing SMB team.&amp;nbsp; In this role, you will manage the full sales cycle, including researching new opportunities and qualifying inbound leads, conducting product demonstrations, negotiating deals, and closing new business. You will work closely with the Sales and Marketing teams to drive lead conversion in a dynamic market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated team player with a high level of technical competencies, ability to exceed goals and motivated by career advancement. We promote from within by hiring exceptional SMB Reps that have the desire and drive to advance to an Enterprise level position within a couple of years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a fully remote position. Candidates can be located anywhere in the U.S., but work hours are aligned with Eastern Standard Time business hours.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
